'''Veronica Ryder''' (born 1955) is an American truck driver and animal activist. She was the owner of [[Joy (cat; V2)|Joy]], a Himalayan cat, who shared a loving relationship with her, unlike her husband, [[Lil Mountjoy (V2)|Lil Mountjoy]]. 

==Early life==
While her exact birthday is unknown, some sources claim that Veronica was born during the Montgomery bus boycott in Alabama in 1955.

